<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
When counting things or expressing a quantity Japanese uses counter words. The counter follows the noun and its
particle and is usually put before the verb it modifies.
</p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
